title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show  DEC-06-2013 FRI
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show  DEC-06-2013 FRI






Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20131206  3 Open Lines

Prager H3: Per usual, callers set the agenda.

 Issues raised include:

    what should Dennis name his autobiography;
     should Dennis live stream his show on video;
      is it ethical to juice up your electrical car at a public school;
        is a voice recording more memorable than a photograph.





Prager 20131206  2 Happiness Hour: Happy in a Grim World

Prager H2: How does one manage a happy attitude when surrounded with so much bad news?
          Dennis has suggestions.  
                                  So do callers.





Prager 20131206  1 Mandela
